    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "BOISE, March 13.-Further hear\ning in the Meyer, Haywood and\nPettibone case was postponed until\nMonday when it is expected the\nsupreme courts ruling on their ap-\npeal will be delivered in court. Mo-\nton for dismissal of the defendants\nwill then be argued. The accused\nmen look well and are in good\nspirits."
    }
